      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The last of the damage actions\nagainst the Great Northern growing\nout of the fearful wreck at Division\nstreet on the early morning of June\n% was filed this morning with the\ncounty clerk. In this action Edmund\nNJ. White. 20 years of age. sues for\n$4,000, alleging partial loss of eye\nsight with prospect of total blind\nness as the years go on. Whites\nmother has already sued the road\nfor damages caused by the loss of her\nminor sons services. but in this case\nthe man sues for permanent DANA ges\nto himself"
    }
  ]
